column5: had my new to me boat out caught some perch but now I see a week later that I have what looks like dried xcales stuck on the seats i  have tried few things with no luck getting them off looking for ideas
Spray 9 is an excellent cleaner for vinyl - not sure about fish scales though.  Gentle rubbing with a stiff brush?
VIM. Works wonders on boat seats and vinyl.
spray with some plain old tap water, leave soaking for 15 minutes, wipe of with a rag, you might have to scape off a few with a dull knife.
